%% ============================================================
%%  EDU System – State Diagram
%%  Entity: Student Application Lifecycle
%% ============================================================
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Unregistered : Student visits EDU platform

    %% Registration
    Unregistered --> Registered : Student creates account
    Registered --> ProfileIncomplete : Logs in for first time

    ProfileIncomplete --> SchoolTypeSelected : Student picks school type
    SchoolTypeSelected --> ResultsEntered    : Student inputs grades/results
    ResultsEntered --> DocumentsUploaded     : Uploads transcripts & certificates
    DocumentsUploaded --> ProfileComplete    : All data validated ✅

    %% Search & matching
    ProfileComplete --> Searching : Student triggers university search
    Searching --> MatchesFound   : System auto-matches universities
    Searching --> NoMatches      : No universities match criteria
    NoMatches --> Searching      : Student adjusts filters / updates results

    %% Chat
    MatchesFound --> Browsing : Student reviews matched universities
    Browsing --> ChatInitiated : Student opens chat with university rep
    ChatInitiated --> WaitingForReply : Message sent to rep
    WaitingForReply --> ChatActive : Rep responds
    ChatActive --> WaitingForReply : Student sends follow-up
    ChatActive --> ChatClosed : Student ends conversation
    ChatClosed --> Browsing : Student returns to listings

    %% Bookmarking & comparing
    Browsing --> Bookmarked : Student saves a university
    Bookmarked --> Comparing : Student adds to comparison list
    Comparing --> Browsing : Student continues searching

    %% Application
    Browsing --> ApplicationDraft : Student clicks "Apply Now"
    Bookmarked --> ApplicationDraft : Student applies from bookmarks
    ApplicationDraft --> ApplicationSubmitted : Student confirms & submits

    ApplicationSubmitted --> UnderReview : University rep reviews application
    UnderReview --> AdditionalDocsRequested : Rep requests more documents
    AdditionalDocsRequested --> UnderReview : Student uploads requested docs
    UnderReview --> Accepted : Application approved 🎉
    UnderReview --> Rejected : Application declined

    Accepted --> EnrollmentPending : Student receives acceptance email
    EnrollmentPending --> Enrolled : Student confirms enrollment
    EnrollmentPending --> Declined : Student declines the offer

    Rejected --> Browsing : Student searches for another university
    Declined --> Browsing : Student looks for alternatives

    Enrolled --> [*] : Process complete ✅
    Declined --> [*]

    note right of MatchesFound
        System ranks universities
        by compatibility score
        based on student grades.
    end note

    note right of ChatInitiated
        FAQ Bot handles common
        questions automatically.
        Rep handles complex ones.
    end note

    note right of Accepted
        Acceptance notification
        sent via Email & SMS.
    end note
